    <h1 class="text-center mb-5">GDPR Article 27 Representative<br />Agreement</h1>
    <div class="alert alert-info alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
      After agreeing to the terms, you will receive by email a secured link to download the signed document.
      <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
        <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
      </button>
    </div>
    <p>This GDPR Article 27 Representative Agreement (this “Agreement”) is entered into by and between the “Company”, and the “Designee”, and together with the Company, the “Parties”, and each a “Party”.</p>
    <table class="table text-left">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th scope="col" style="width: 34%"></th>
          <th scope="col" style="width: 33%">COMPANY</th>
